<section class="emizentech-faq">
<div class="container">
<div class="section-title">
<h2><span>FAQs</span></h2>
<p>Fantasy Sports App Development FAQ</p>
</div>
<div class="faq-wrap">
<div id="accordion">
<div class="card">
<div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
<button class="btn btn-link" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
I want to know the exact cost of fantasy sports app development?
</button>
</div>
<div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordion">
<div class="card-body">
<p>The cost of a fantasy sports application entirely depends on the extensiveness and intricacy of your requirements. We cannot depict the fixed cost unless we analyze your requirements meticulously.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
<button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
Will you provide me the source code of fantasy sports app?
</button>
</div>
<div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordion">
<div class="card-body">
<p>Yes, we will surely provide you the source code of fantasy sports app but you need to hire an expert developer to modify it.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
<button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
Will the actual fantasy sports app will be similar to the demo app?
</button>
</div>
<div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordion">
<div class="card-body">
<p>We lay great emphasis on the quality and functionality of the end product. The fantasy sports app will be similar to the demo app in every aspect unless changes asked from your end.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<div class="card-header" id="headingFour">
<button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
Why Should I go for the Emizentech Fantasy Sports App?
</button>
</div>
<div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordion">
<div class="card-body">
<p>When it comes to providing a potent and highly engaging fantasy sports app, we are second to none. Our application is packed with all state-of-the-art features and other advanced features that are required to give your audience an enthralling betting experience like they never had before. Moreover, with some additional cost, we can also integrate those features that you will rarely find in other applications.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<div class="card-header" id="headingFive">
<button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
What technologies you use to develop the fantasy sports application?
</button>
</div>
<div id="collapseFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-parent="#accordion">
<div class="card-body">
<p>We use only the latest, most potent, and efficient technologies to develop the fantasy sports application that fits your requirements. For mobile applications, we use technologies like Android SDK Emulator, MobiOne, and Android Sketch Paper. For developing a fantasy sports iOS application, we use Xamarin, RhoMobile, and Appcelerator.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

